flowchart TD
  producer[Producer keyed by trip_id] --> kafka[(trip-state)]
  kafka --> server[Realtime consuming segment]
  server --> compare{Higher comparisonColumns value?}
  compare -->|yes| replace[replace latest row]
  compare -->|no| drop[drop stale row]
  replace --> snapshot[optional snapshot persistence]
  replace --> query[query latest state]
  drop --> metrics[stale row metrics]
